This is pushed to docker.internal.sysdig.com/agent-helpers/prometheus-generator:latest
by the agent-build-postsubmit job.

------

To build the container yourself, cd into the prometheus-generator directory and call

> docker build -t prometheus-generator:latest .

Add this to your config

prometheus:
  enabled: true
  process_filter:
    - include:
        port: 5005

and run

> docker run -d -p 5005:5005 prometheus-generator


OR alternatively add just this to your config

prometheus:
  enabled: true

and run

> docker run -d -p 5005:5005 -l io.prometheus.scrape=true -l io.prometheus.port=5005 prometheus-generator
